{"tid":624991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"777稱「禁單程證人士來港便無房屋問題」想法不切實際","createTime":"2018-04-11T05:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T08:11:40.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d10a6cab4b6f499b655e0dd1c1e03adc1cff49bf","tid":624991,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席立法會行政長官質詢時間時表示，房屋問題是今屆政府的重中之重，知道現時未能回應市民期望。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回應工聯會郭偉強的提問時表示，以新一期居屋預料會超額認購幾十倍為例，反映房屋供不應求，明顯有剛性需求。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人反對開拓土地，指只要禁止每日150名持單程證人士到港，便會沒有房屋問題，林鄭月娥批評，有關想法是不切實際、混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，房屋供應量近年持續下降，現時大幅落後進度，唯有大量開拓土地，才能回應市民期盼。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390605-20180411.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390605-20180411.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=a3%2FA6laLgyZZ0mbNJ%2FLrwozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=287a4948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390605-20180411.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=540ebae7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390605-20180411.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0258c5c75656ca6c635a3d52dc84653e28bacef4","tid":624991,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"正路應該係將97年後嚟嘅低端人口趕返上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aff94933396e0a5a61d83fbe5a8e97c108e64e7","tid":624991,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"不切實際你唔好住屋企唔好住官邸搬去公屋住囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633f5512dbe59afebdbd1603aeb302f7d5e5b87d","tid":624991,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"岩，做唔到既野諗來係不切實際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\